<main id="main">
<header id="title"><h1>
<center>The Life of Mohandas Karamchand Gandhi</h1>
<h3> <center> The pioneer of the nonviolent freedom movement in India </h3>
</header>
<hr>
<div id="img-div">
<figure>
<img src="http://img.timeinc.net/time/daily/2008/0805/360_gandhi_topics_0528.jpg" id="image" alt="A picture of Mahatma Gandhi">
</div>
</figure>
